title: Batman/Catwoman - Trail of the Gun 01-02 (2004|Digital|ZK-E)
description:
Promotional blurb from ComiXology - "Bat and Cat collide when the entire criminal underground goes after a gun that never misses. Catwoman wants the weapon for herself--a testament to her abilities and title as the world's greatest thief--but Batman wants to see the deadly firearm gone for good!"

Written by the great Ann Nocenti with art by Ethan Van Sciver. This torrent contains both issues in digital format thanks to ZoneKing-Empire. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
